2.1.2.1.4 Exercise JSON Schema
{
    "$schema": "http://json-schema.org/draft-04/schema#",
    "type": "object",
    "title": "Exercise",
    "additionalProperties": false,
    "properties": {
        "exercise_id": {
            "type": "string",
            "pattern": "^[a-fA-F0-9]{24}$"
        },
        "name": {
            "type": "string"
        },
        "description": {
            "type": "string"
        },
        "n_min_rep": {
            "type": "number"
        },
        "n_max_rep": {
            "type": "number"
        },
        "time": {
            "type": "number"
        },
        "to_failure": {
            "type": "boolean"
        },
        "video_url": {
            "type": "string"
        },
        "muscles": {
            "type": "array",
            "additionalItems": true,
            "uniqueItems": false,
            "items": {
                "type": "string",
                "pattern": "^[a-fA-F0-9]{24}$"
            }
        },
        "category": {
            "type": "string"
        },
        "equipment": {
            "type": "string"
        },
        "exercise_imgs": {
            "type": "array",
            "additionalItems": true,
            "uniqueItems": false,
            "items": {
                "type": "string"
            }
        },
        "points": {
            "type": "number"
        }
    },
    "required": [
        "exercise_id",
        "name",
        "description"
    ]
}

2.1.2.1.6 Exercise Target Script
use lets_workout_db;

db.createCollection( "Exercise",{
    "storageEngine": {
        "wiredTiger": {}
    },
    "capped": false,
    "validator": {
        "$jsonSchema": {
            "bsonType": "object",
            "title": "Exercise",
            "additionalProperties": false,
            "properties": {
                "_id": {
                    "bsonType": "objectId"
                },
                "exercise_id": {
                    "bsonType": "objectId"
                },
                "name": {
                    "bsonType": "string"
                },
                "description": {
                    "bsonType": "string"
                },
                "n_min_rep": {
                    "bsonType": "number"
                },
                "n_max_rep": {
                    "bsonType": "number"
                },
                "time": {
                    "bsonType": "number"
                },
                "to_failure": {
                    "bsonType": "bool"
                },
                "video_url": {
                    "bsonType": "string"
                },
                "muscles": {
                    "bsonType": "array",
                    "additionalItems": true,
                    "uniqueItems": false,
                    "items": {
                        "bsonType": "objectId"
                    }
                },
                "category": {
                    "bsonType": "string"
                },
                "equipment": {
                    "bsonType": "string"
                },
                "exercise_imgs": {
                    "bsonType": "array",
                    "additionalItems": true,
                    "uniqueItems": false,
                    "items": {
                        "bsonType": "binData"
                    }
                },
                "points": {
                    "bsonType": "number"
                }
            },
            "required": [
                "exercise_id",
                "name",
                "description"
            ]
        }
    },
    "validationLevel": "off",
    "validationAction": "warn"
});

            "additionalProperties": false,
            "properties": {
                "_id": {
                    "bsonType": "objectId"
                },
                "name": {
                    "bsonType": "string"
                },
                "image": {
                    "bsonType": "binData"
                },
                "muscle_id": {
                    "bsonType": "objectId"
                }
            },
            "required": [
